channel.description:
This contains all of the original interfaces from a clean #317 cache.
[B]Format[/B]
interfaceId_groupId.png [B] Group Ids[/B] [CODE] public static final int TYPE_CONTAINER = 0; public static final int TYPE_INVENTORY = 2; public static final int TYPE_ITEM_LIST = 7; public static final int TYPE_MODEL = 6; public static final int TYPE_MODEL_LIST = 1; public static final int TYPE_RECTANGLE = 3; public static final int TYPE_SPRITE = 5; public static final int TYPE_TEXT = 4; [/CODE]
These are all 0 if you haven't noticed which means they are a container that holds sub interfaces that has children on them.
For a dump of only the children visit [URL=http://"https://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/downloads/632255-317-interface-sprite-dump.html"]here[/URL].
